<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/41427852-brenda-williamson"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1426950691i/41427852._UX100_CR0,11,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/41427852-brenda-williamson">Brenda Williamson</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This little book changed my life forever. It changed my understanding of everything that I had ever believed about Jesus. I would recommend this book <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This little book changed my life forever. It changed my understanding of everything that I had ever believed about Jesus. I would recommend this book to anyone who feels unworthy of the love of Christ. His radical love for you will in turn, change your affections. I read this book many years ago, following the end of a 22 year marriage. I was never the same after reading this little book. Prior to reading it, I prayed to die. Silly now, but not so silly at the time.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
